  "texts": [
    "Therefore, IAA was measured for the outcomes of both annotation phases, and the results are presented in Table 2.",
    "In the Initial annotation phase, the IAA scores for strict constraints related to TF and disease mentions Table 2.",
    "IAA scores for entities and relations in the TFDR corpus.",
    "were 0.949 and 0.781, respectively.",
    "However, for the relaxed constraints, the IAA values showed improvement, reaching 0.958 for TF mentions and 0.821 for disease mentions."
  ]
}